55 KM NE of Morondava via route 8 at the forestry concession of the Centre de Formation Professional Forestière (CFPF), Kirindy Forest. Between 5 and 5.5 KM E of route 8 on the principal concession road (Piste CONOCO), along S boundary of forestry block CN5. Dry deciduous forest with Adansonia grandidieri, Colvillea sp., Terminalia sp., and Grewia sp. dominants. Collected with D.K. Harder, E.A. Rakotobe, T.G. Razafindrabeaza & J.P. Abraham.
